{voice
 {:nses [com.blockether.vis.ext.voice.core]
  :description "Native local voice extension: Piper TTS output and Parakeet ASR input through sherpa-onnx."
  :docs [{:title "Voice"
          :content "Adds local text-to-speech with Piper and local voice input with Parakeet ASR. Piper model directory defaults to ~/.vis/models/sherpa-onnx-vits-piper-en_US-ryan-high and can be overridden with VIS_PIPER_MODEL_DIR. Parakeet model directory defaults to ~/.vis/models/sherpa-onnx-nemo-parakeet-tdt-0.6b-v3-int8 and can be overridden with VIS_PARAKEET_MODEL_DIR. Missing model files can be downloaded with vis extensions voice models download."}]}}
